Server-side (DataAnnotations)
•	[Required] — name, weight, parent selection
•	[Range(0.0001, double.MaxValue)] — weight > 0
•	[StringLength(200)] — name length cap
•	[EmailAddress] — login email format
•	[MinLength(6)] — password minimum

11.2 Business Rule Validation (Repository)
•	Total child weight must not exceed parent weight
•	Parent item must exist before processing
•	At least one valid child item required
•	Transaction rollback on any failure — data integrity guaranteed

11.3 Client-side (jQuery Unobtrusive Validation)
•	Enabled via ClientValidationEnabled and UnobtrusiveJavaScriptEnabled in Web.config
•	Live weight bar shows remaining capacity before form submission
•	JSON child data collected client-side and passed as hidden field
